{"tid":1094625,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"估國家~父涉兩度性侵女兒　因「難確認無力抵抗」獲改判無罪","createTime":"2019-04-06T12:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T05:36:28.000Z","uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8b708092e1d9c7736499991e0701026f32d2ba3c","tid":1094625,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:24:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190406/photo/bkn-20190406110244941-0406_00912_001_01p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190406110244941-0406_00912_001_01p.jpg&h=4ac78c9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n名古屋地方法院岡崎分院法官裁定被告無罪。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n日本愛知縣一名父親涉嫌兩度性侵女兒，前年被控強制性交罪，檢察官向法院要求重判被告10年監禁。但名古屋地方法院岡崎分院日前卻以「無法確認女事主處於無力抵抗的狀態」，改判疑犯無罪。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n控方指，事主自國中二年級開始遭父親性虐待，但因父親協助支付就讀專門學校的費用，令她無法拒絕。被告前年8月及9月分別在公司及酒店，與當時19歲的女兒發生性行為。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前法院判決認定性侵事實，指父親違反女兒意願，並令她失去抵抗意願。然而，岡崎分院法官上月26日認為，由於兩人發生性行為時無法確認女方是否心懷恐懼，她過往亦曾拒絕父親騷擾，並在弟弟幫助下迴避，因此難以證明事主沒有能力抗拒，故裁定被告無罪。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190406/photo/bkn-20190406110244941-0406_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190406110401\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20190406%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190406110244941-0406_00912_001_01p.jpg%3F20190406110401&d=174aH8n0e8hd5Ixdtq%2FhYlFFw%2Fpr%2F0Xu32W9HouEUHQ%3D&h=bca8c355\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20190406/photo/bkn-20190406110244941-0406_00912_001_01p.jpg?20190406110401</a>"},{"pid":"47793eb36605418774e915eebea0e1d216767252","tid":1094625,"uid":18456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:36:16.000Z","msg":"仲諗住有得睇祟日撚解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccc4e7d8ed357bc1b151a8a940a16d2efe382c3","tid":1094625,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-06T12:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9a58f437b90f019ad5ce6e292d4bdd31ab22cd","tid":1094625,"uid":141060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:16:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48272603c31231d6efb04bde86dff3850eb430cf","tid":1094625,"uid":62506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-07T05:36:28.000Z","msg":"日本亂倫唔犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}